<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8345356>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34–42. Lomechusoides mongolicus Wasmann, 1897. 34, female lectotype, dorsal habitus; 35, female lectotype, pronotum in dorsal view (L: 1.15 mm, W: 1.75 mm); 36, male, microstructure of elytra with setation, (locality: Primorsky territory, about 40 km WSW from Vladiwostok); 37, male, aedeagus, lateral view; 38, male, aedeagus, ventral view; 39, male, metaventral process; 40, male, apex of paramere [Figs. 37–40 (locality: China: Inner Mongolia: Donkyra, pass Djusso)]; 41, female lectotype, spermatheca, (locality: Mongolia: Changai); 42, female, spermatheca, (locality: East Siberia: Irkutsk area). Scale bars in mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8345356/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

